<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>@ViewBag.Title</title>
    <link href="~/Content/css/posterWall.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="~/Content/css/850_24_col.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <script src="~/Content/scripts/jquery-1.7.1.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="page-wrapperTop"></div>
    <div class="page-wrapper">


            @RenderBody()


        <section class="footer container_24" id="pw-footer">

            <div class="grid_10">
                <h2>WHAT'S THIS ALL ABOUT?</h2>
                <p>So, this is just a bit of fun .. a doff of the cap to the original posters.</p>
                <p>Here you can create the posters which could have been.</p>

                <h2>GUIDELINES</h2>
                <p>Please have fun and enjoy the site in the manor which was intended.</p>
                <p>Post responsibly, please don't loose your job! .. REMEMBER YOU ARE RESPONSIBLE FOR WHAT YOU POST.</p>
                <p>OK, got it! <input type="checkbox" /></p>

                <h2>LOGIN</h2>
                <input type="text" id="userName" class="login" placeholder="UserName" />
                <input type="text" id="password" class="login" placeholder="Password" />
                <a href="#">register</a>
            </div>

            <div class="grid_14">
                <h2>CREATE</h2>
                @{ Html.RenderPartial("_createPoster", new VivaRevolution.Models.ViewModels.PosterViewModel()); }
            </div>

        </section>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
